msgstr "Pisava določene širine"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1004
msgid "Name of the default font with fixed character width."
msgstr "Ime privzete pisave določene širine."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1010
msgid "Variable font name"
msgstr "Pisava spremenljive širine"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1011
msgid "Name of the default font with variable character width."
msgstr "Ime privzete pisave spremenljive širine."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1017
msgid "Display hex offset"
msgstr "Pokaži šestnajstiški zamik"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1018
msgid "This option defines if the hexadecimal offset should be displayed in hex mode."
msgstr "Možnost določa šestnajstiški odmik notranjega pregledovalnika v šestnajstiškem načinu pogleda."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1024
msgid "Wrap mode"
msgstr "Način preloma"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1025
msgid "This option defines if too long text lines should be wrapped."
msgstr "Možnost določa, ali naj se predolge besedilne vrstice prelomijo po določenem številu znakov."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1031
msgid "Font size"
msgstr "Velikost pisave"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1032
msgid "This option defines the default font size."
msgstr "Možnost določa privzeto velikost pisave."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1038
msgid "Tab size"
msgstr "Velikost zamika tabulatorja"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1039
msgid "This option defines the indentation width in terms of characters for a tabulator character."
msgstr "Možnost določa širino zamika kot število znakov za znake tabulatorja."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1045
msgid "Bytes per line in binary mode"
msgstr "Število bajtov v vrstici v dvojiškem načinu"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1046
msgid "This option defines how many bytes should be displayed in one line in binary mode."
msgstr "Možnost določa velikost prikazane vrstice dvojiškega izpisa v bajtih."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1052
msgid "Metadata view"
msgstr "Metapodatkovni pogled"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1053
msgid "This option defines if metadata should be visible."
msgstr "Možnost določa, ali naj bodo metapodatki prikazani."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1059
msgid "Window width"
msgstr "Širina okna"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1060
msgid "The width of the internal file viewer window."
msgstr "Določa širino okna notranjega pregledovalnika."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1066
msgid "Window height"
msgstr "Višina okna"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1067
msgid "The height of the internal file viewer window."
msgstr "Določa višino okna notranjega pregledovalnika."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1073
msgid "Search pattern for text"
msgstr "Iskalni niz besedila"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1074
msgid "This string array stores the history of text searches within the internal file viewer."
msgstr "Niz določa shranjeno zgodovino besedilnih iskanj v notranjem pregledovalniku datotek."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1080
msgid "Search pattern for hex values"
msgstr "Iskalni niz šestnajstiške vrednosti"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1081
msgid "This string array stores the history of searches for hex values within the internal file viewer."
msgstr ""
"Niz določa shranjeno zgodovina iskanj za šestnajstiške vrednosti v notranjem pregledovalniku datotek."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1089
msgid "File suffix"
msgstr "Pripona datoteke"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1090
msgid "Default file suffix of archives created with the File Roller plugin."
msgstr "Privzeta pripona arhivov, ki so ustvarjeni z vstavkom File Roller."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1096
msgid "Prefix pattern"
msgstr "Vzorec predpone"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1097
msgid "The prefix pattern is used to build up the name for an archive created with the File Roller plugin."
msgstr "Vzorec predpone se uporablja za izgradnjo imena arhiva, ustvarjenega z vstavkom File Roller."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1105
msgid "Automatically loaded plugins"
msgstr "Samodejno naloži vstavke"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.gschema.xml:1106
msgid ""
"This is the list of automatically loaded plugins, whereas each entry represents the file name of the "
"plugin."
msgstr "To je seznam samodejno naloženih vstavkov, vsak vnos pa predstavlja ime datoteke tega vstavka."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.metainfo.xml.in:17
msgid "Dual-panel file manager"
msgstr "Dvostrani urejevalnik datotek"

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.metainfo.xml.in:19
msgid ""
"GNOME Commander is a “dual-panel” graphical file manager for the GNOME desktop environment. It features "
"separate tabs for each panel, setting up custom device buttons, bookmark manager, fully integrated "
"commandline, file quick search, an internal image viewer, a powerful batch renaming tool, and FTP and "
"Samba access."
msgstr ""
"Gnome Commander je »dvostrani« upravljalnik datotek za namizje GNOME. Omogoča ločene zavihke za vsako "
"podokno, določitev gumbov naprav po meri, upravitelja zaznamkov, v celoti integrirano ukazno vrstico, "
"hitro iskanje datotek, vgrajeni pregledovalnik slik in zmogljivo orodje za paketno preimenovanje. Podpira "
"tudi različne protokole dostopa do oddaljene vsebine od FTP do Sambe."

#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.metainfo.xml.in:26
msgid ""
"GNOME Commander aims to advanced users who like to focus on precise file management, working in parallel "
"through special applications, and running smart commands."
msgstr ""
"Program GNOME Commander je namenjen naprednim uporabnikom, ki želijo imeti pregled nad datotekami, "
"opravljati več nalog hkrati in izvajati naprednejša datotečna opravila."

#. developer_name tag deprecated with Appstream 1.0
#: data/org.gnome.gnome-commander.metainfo.xml.in:57
msgid "The GNOME Project"
msgstr "Projekt GNOME"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:63 plugins/taglib/taglib-plugin.cc:70
msgid "Album"
msgstr "Album"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:63
msgid "Name of an album the image belongs to."
msgstr "Ime albuma, ki mu pripada spodnja slika."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:64
msgid "Make"
msgstr "Izvedba"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:64
msgid "Make of camera used to take the image."
msgstr "Izvedba aparata s katerim je bila zajeta slika."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:65 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:158
msgid "Model"
msgstr "Model"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:65
msgid "Model of camera used to take the image."
msgstr "Model aparata s katerim je bila zajeta slika."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:66 plugins/gsf/gsf-plugin.cc:80
msgid "Comments"
msgstr "_Opombe"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:66 plugins/gsf/gsf-plugin.cc:80
msgid "User definable free text."
msgstr "Uporabniško določeno prosto besedilo."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:67 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:86 plugins/taglib/taglib-plugin.cc:78
#: plugins/taglib/taglib-plugin.cc:171
msgid "Copyright"
msgstr "Avtorske pravice"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:67
msgid "Embedded copyright message."
msgstr "Vstavljeno sporočilo avtorstva."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:68 plugins/gsf/gsf-plugin.cc:65
msgid "Creator"
msgstr "Ustvarjalec"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:68 plugins/gsf/gsf-plugin.cc:64 plugins/poppler/poppler-plugin.cc:60
msgid "Name of the author."
msgstr "Ime avtorja."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:69 plugins/taglib/taglib-plugin.cc:173
#: src/advanced_rename/advanced_rename_dialog.rs:417 src/advanced_rename/profile_component.rs:208
#: src/advanced_rename/profile_component.rs:662
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Datum"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:69
msgid "Datetime image was originally created."
msgstr "Datum in čas nastanka slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:70 plugins/gsf/gsf-plugin.cc:68 plugins/taglib/taglib-plugin.cc:337
#: src/file_metainfo_view.rs:66 src/tags/basic.rs:58
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:70
msgid "Description of the image."
msgstr "Opis slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:71 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:90
msgid "Exposure Program"
msgstr "Program osvetlitve"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:71
msgid ""
"The program used by the camera to set exposure when the picture is taken. EG Manual, Normal, Aperture "
"priority etc."
msgstr ""
"Program, ki ga uporablja kamera za določitev osvetlitve ob zajemanju slike. EG ročni, običajni, Prednost "
"zaslonke in podobno."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:72 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:127
msgid "Exposure Time"
msgstr "Čas osvetlitve"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:72
msgid "Exposure time used to capture the photo in seconds."
msgstr "Čas osvetlitve med zajemanjem slike v sekundah."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:73 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:91
msgid "Flash"
msgstr "Flash"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:73
msgid "Set to “1” if flash was fired."
msgstr "Vrednost » 1 «, če je bila slika narejena s sproženo bliskavico."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:74 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:93
msgid "F Number"
msgstr "F število"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:74 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:93
msgid "Diameter of the aperture relative to the effective focal length of the lens."
msgstr "Premer zaslonke določen relativno na žariščno dolžino leče."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:75 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:94
msgid "Focal Length"
msgstr "Goriščna razdalja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:75
msgid "Focal length of lens in mm."
msgstr "Žariščna razdalja leče v milimetrih."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:76
msgid "ISO Speed"
msgstr "Hitrost ISO"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:76
msgid "ISO speed used to acquire the document contents. For example, 100, 200, 400, etc."
msgstr "Hitrost ISO za dostop do vsebine dokumenta. Vrednosti 100, 200, 400, etc."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:77 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:213 plugins/gsf/gsf-plugin.cc:70
#: plugins/poppler/poppler-plugin.cc:59 src/tags/basic.rs:59
msgid "Keywords"
msgstr "Ključne besede"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:77
msgid "String of keywords."
msgstr "Niz ključnih besed."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:78 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:97
msgid "Metering Mode"
msgstr "Način umerjanja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:78
msgid ""
"Metering mode used to acquire the image (IE Unknown, Average, CenterWeightedAverage, Spot, MultiSpot, "
"Pattern, Partial)."
msgstr ""
"Način merjenja, ki se uporablja pri pridobivanju slike (neznano, povprečno, vzorčno, delno, točkovno, "
"večtočkovno)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:79 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:162
msgid "Orientation"
msgstr "Usmerjenost"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:79
msgid "Represents the orientation of the image wrt camera (IE “top,left” or “bottom,right”)."
msgstr "Vrednost predstavlja usmerjenost slike (IE »zgoraj,levo« ali »spodaj,desno«)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:80 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:179
msgid "Software"
msgstr "Programska oprema"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:80
msgid "Software used to produce/enhance the image."
msgstr "Programska oprema uporabljena za izdelavo ali pripravo slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:81 plugins/gsf/gsf-plugin.cc:66 plugins/poppler/poppler-plugin.cc:57
#: plugins/taglib/taglib-plugin.cc:96
msgid "Title"
msgstr "Naslov"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:81
msgid "Title of image."
msgstr "Naslov slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:82 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:99
msgid "White Balance"
msgstr "Uravnoteženje beline"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:82
msgid "White balance setting of the camera when the picture was taken (auto or manual)."
msgstr "Nastavitev beline aparata med zajemanjem slike (samodejno ali ročno)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:83 src/tags/image.rs:30
msgid "Width"
msgstr "Širina"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:83 src/tags/image.rs:38
msgid "Width in pixels."
msgstr "Širina v točkah."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:84 src/tags/image.rs:31
msgid "Height"
msgstr "Višina"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:84 src/tags/image.rs:39
msgid "Height in pixels."
msgstr "Višina v točkah."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:86
msgid ""
"Copyright information. The tag is used to indicate both the photographer and editor copyrights. It is the "
"copyright notice of the person or organization claiming rights to the image. The Interoperability "
"copyright statement including date and rights should be written in this field; e.g., “Copyright, John "
"Smith, 19xx. All rights reserved.”. The field records both the photographer and editor copyrights, with "
"each recorded in a separate part of the statement. When there is a clear distinction between the "
"photographer and editor copyrights, these are to be written in the order of photographer followed by "
"editor copyright, separated by NULL (in this case, since the statement also ends with a NULL, there are "
"two NULL codes) (see example 1). When only the photographer is given, it is terminated by one NULL code. "
"When only the editor copyright is given, the photographer copyright part consists of one space followed "
"by a terminating NULL code, then the editor copyright is given. When the field is left blank, it is "
"treated as unknown."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnosti lastništva. Oznaka določa tako lastništvo fotografa kot tudi urednika. Lastništvo mora biti "
"vpisano popolno z vsemi pripadajočimi podatki; primer: »Lastništvo, Janez Novak, 19xx. Vse pravice "
"pridržane.«. Polje vključuje lastništva vseh sodelujočih, podatki pa morajo biti zapisani na ločenih "
"delih. Kadar so avtorske pravice jasno ločene, morajo biti zabeležene od fotografa, do oblikovalcev in "
"naprej in se morajo ločiti z vrednostjo NULL (v tem primeru sta na koncu dve vrednosti NULL, oglejte si "
"primer 1). Kadar pa je lastništvo vezano le na fotografa, se konča z enojno NULL kodo. Prazno polje se "
"obravnava kot neznan podatek lastništva."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:87
msgid "Date and Time"
msgstr "Datum in čas"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:87
msgid "The date and time of image creation."
msgstr "Datum in čas zajetja slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:88
msgid "Exposure Bias"
msgstr "Nagnjenost osvetlitve"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:88
msgid ""
"The exposure bias. The units is the APEX value. Ordinarily it is given in the range of -99.99 to 99.99."
msgstr "Vrednosti nagnjenosti osvetlitve so v APEX enotah. Običajno se vrednost giblje med -99.99 in 99.99."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:89
msgid "Exposure Mode"
msgstr "Način osvetlitve"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:89
msgid ""
"The exposure mode set when the image was shot. In auto-bracketing mode, the camera shoots a series of "
"frames of the same scene at different exposure settings."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka določa način osvetlitve ob zajetju slike. V načinu samodejnega prilagajanja (auto-bracketing), "
"aparat zajame nekaj zaporednih slik z različnimi nastavitvami osvetlitve."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:90
msgid "The class of the program used by the camera to set exposure when the picture is taken."
msgstr "Program fotoaparata, ki je bil uporabljen pri osvetljevanju slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:91
msgid "This tag is recorded when an image is taken using a strobe light (flash)."
msgstr "Podatki oznake se shranijo, kadar je slika zajeta z osvetljevanjem z bliskavico."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:92
msgid "Flash Energy"
msgstr "Flash energija"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:92
msgid ""
"The strobe energy at the time the image is captured, as measured in Beam Candle Power Seconds (BCPS)."
msgstr "Energija bliskavice ob zajetju slike, izmerjene v BCPS (Beam Candle Power Seconds)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:94
msgid ""
"The actual focal length of the lens, in mm. Conversion is not made to the focal length of a 35 mm film "
"camera."
msgstr ""
"Dejanska žariščna razdalja leče v milimetrih. Pretvorba ne velja za žariščno razdaljo 35 mm filmske "
"kamere."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:95
msgid "ISO Speed Ratings"
msgstr "Ocena ISO hitrosti"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:95
msgid "The ISO Speed and ISO Latitude of the camera or input device as specified in ISO 12232."
msgstr "Hitrost ISO in širina ISO aparata ali druge vhodne naprave kot to določa standard ISO 12232."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:96
msgid "Max Aperture Value"
msgstr "Največja vrednost zaslonke"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:96
msgid ""
"The smallest F number of the lens. The unit is the APEX value. Ordinarily it is given in the range of "
"00.00 to 99.99, but it is not limited to this range."
msgstr ""
"Najmanjša goriščna (F) razdalja leče. Enota je v APEX vrednostih. Običajno je podana v območju med 00.00 "
"in 99.99, vendar na to območje ni omejena."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:97
msgid "The metering mode."
msgstr "Način umerjanja."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:98
msgid "Shutter Speed"
msgstr "Hitrost zaklopke"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:98
msgid "Shutter speed. The unit is the APEX (Additive System of Photographic Exposure) setting."
msgstr "Hitrost zaklopke. Enota predstavlja APEX vrednost (Additive System of Photographic Exposure)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:99
msgid "The white balance mode set when the image was shot."
msgstr "Način beline določen med zajemanjem slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:100
msgid "Pixel X Dimension"
msgstr "Dimenzija točke X"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:100
msgid ""
"Information specific to compressed data. When a compressed file is recorded, the valid width of the "
"meaningful image must be recorded in this tag, whether or not there is padding data or a restart marker. "
"This tag should not exist in an uncompressed file."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnosti posebej določene za stisnjene podatke. Kadar je shranjena stisnjena datoteka, mora biti "
"veljavna širina slike zabeležena v oznaki, neodvisno od ostalih podatkov in markerjev. Oznaka ne sme biti "
"na voljo pri nestisnjenih zapisih slik."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:101
msgid "Pixel Y Dimension"
msgstr "Dimenzija točke Y"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:101
msgid ""
"Information specific to compressed data. When a compressed file is recorded, the valid height of the "
"meaningful image must be recorded in this tag, whether or not there is padding data or a restart marker. "
"This tag should not exist in an uncompressed file. Since data padding is unnecessary in the vertical "
"direction, the number of lines recorded in this valid image height tag will in fact be the same as that "
"recorded in the SOF."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnosti posebej določene za stisnjene podatke. Kadar je shranjena stisnjena datoteka, mora biti "
"veljavna višina slike zabeležena v oznaki, neodvisno od ostalih podatkov in markerjev. Oznaka ne sme biti "
"na voljo pri nestisnjenih zapisih slik. Ker podlaganje podatkov v navpični smeri ni zahtevano, je število "
"vrstic enako shranjeni vrednosti SOF."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:102
msgid "x Resolution"
msgstr "Ločljivost X"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:102
msgid ""
"The number of pixels per <Exif.ResolutionUnit> in the <Exif.ImageWidth> direction. When the image "
"resolution is unknown, 72 [dpi] is designated."
msgstr ""
"Število točk na <Exif.ResolutionUnit> v <Exif.ImageWidth> smeri. Kadar je ločljivost slike znana, je "
"določena vrednost 72 [dpi]."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:103
msgid "y Resolution"
msgstr "Ločljivost Y"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:103
msgid ""
"The number of pixels per <Exif.ResolutionUnit> in the <Exif.ImageLength> direction. The same value as "
"<Exif.XResolution> is designated."
msgstr ""
"Število točk na <Exif.ResolutionUnit> v<Exif.ImageLength> smeri. Uporabljena je enaka vrednost kot pri "
"oznaki<Exif.XResolution>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:104
msgid "Image Length"
msgstr "Dolžina slike"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:104
msgid "The number of rows of image data. In JPEG compressed data a JPEG marker is used instead of this tag."
msgstr "Število vrstic podatkov slike. Pri JPEG stiskanju je uporabljen poseben marker namesto te oznake."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:105
msgid "Image Width"
msgstr "Širina slike"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:105
msgid ""
"The number of columns of image data, equal to the number of pixels per row. In JPEG compressed data a "
"JPEG marker is used instead of this tag."
msgstr ""
"Število stolpcev podatkov slike, ki je enako številu točk na vrstico. Pri JPEG stiskanju je uporabljen "
"poseben marker namesto te oznake."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:106
msgid "Custom Rendered"
msgstr "Izris po meri"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:106
msgid ""
"The use of special processing on image data, such as rendering geared to output. When special processing "
"is performed, the reader is expected to disable or minimize any further processing."
msgstr ""
"Uporaba posebnih učinkov pri obdelavi slike, kot na primer posebni način izrisovanja. V primeru uporabe "
"posebnih učinkov bralnik onemogoči ali zmanjša vse ostale učinke na sliko."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:107
msgid "Color Space"
msgstr "Barvni prostor"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:107
msgid ""
"The color space information tag is always recorded as the color space specifier. Normally sRGB is used to "
"define the color space based on the PC monitor conditions and environment. If a color space other than "
"sRGB is used, Uncalibrated is set. Image data recorded as Uncalibrated can be treated as sRGB when it is "
"converted to FlashPix."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnosti prostora barve je vedno zabeležen kot določilo prostora barve. Običajno je uporabljeno sRGB "
"določilo prostora na osnovi zaslona in okolja. V primeru, da je uporabljen drug sistem namesto sistema "
"sRGB, je določena vrednost neumerjeno. Podatke slike zajete neumerjeno je mogoče obravnavati kot "
"vrednosti sRGB, kadar so vrednosti prevedene v sistem FlashPix."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:108
msgid "Document Name"
msgstr "Ime dokumenta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:108
msgid "Document name."
msgstr "Ime dokumenta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:109
msgid "User Comment"
msgstr "Opomba uporabnika"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:109
msgid ""
"A tag for Exif users to write keywords or comments on the image besides those in <Exif.ImageDescription>, "
"and without the character code limitations of the <Exif.ImageDescription> tag. The character code used in "
"the <Exif.UserComment> tag is identified based on an ID code in a fixed 8-byte area at the start of the "
"tag data area. The unused portion of the area is padded with NULL (“00.h”). ID codes are assigned by "
"means of registration. The value of CountN is determinated based on the 8 bytes in the character code "
"area and the number of bytes in the user comment part. Since the TYPE is not ASCII, NULL termination is "
"not necessary. The ID code for the <Exif.UserComment> area may be a Defined code such as JIS or ASCII, or "
"may be Undefined. The Undefined name is UndefinedText, and the ID code is filled with 8 bytes of all "
"“NULL” (“00.H”). An Exif reader that reads the <Exif.UserComment> tag must have a function for "
"determining the ID code. This function is not required in Exif readers that do not use the "
"<Exif.UserComment> tag. When a <Exif.UserComment> area is set aside, it is recommended that the ID code "
"be ASCII and that the following user comment part be filled with blank characters [20.H]."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka za uporabnike določil Exif, s katerimi je mogoče ob ključnih besedah in komentarjih k sliki "
"zapisati tudi druge oznake <Exif.ImageDescription> in brez omejitev znakovne kode oznake "
"<Exif.ImageDescription>. Znakovna koda, uporabljena v oznaki <Exif.UserComment>, je določena na podlagi "
"identifikacijske kode v stalnem 8-bajtnem območju na začetku podatkovnega območja oznake. Neizkoriščeni "
"del območja je zapolnjen z NULL (\"00.h\"). ID določila se dodelijo z registracijo. Vrednost CountN se "
"določi na podlagi 8 bajtov v območju kod znakov in števila bajtov v delu z uporabniškim komentarjem. Ker "
"TYPE ni ASCII, zaključek NULL ni potreben. ID koda za območje <Exif.UserComment> je lahko opredeljena "
"koda, kot sta JIS ali ASCII, ali pa je nedoločena. Nedoločeno ime je UndefinedText, ID koda pa je "
"napolnjena z 8 bajti vseh \"NULL\" (\"00.H\"). Bralnik Exif, ki bere oznako <Exif.UserComment>, mora "
"imeti funkcijo za določanje kode ID. Ta funkcija ni potrebna v bralnikih Exif, ki ne uporabljajo oznake "
"<Exif.UserComment>. Kadar je območje <Exif.UserComment> rezervirano, je priporočljivo, da je ID koda "
"ASCII in da je naslednji del uporabniškega komentarja izpolnjen s praznimi znaki [20.H]."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:110
msgid "Aperture"
msgstr "Zaslonka"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:110
msgid "The lens aperture. The unit is the APEX value."
msgstr "Zaslonka leče. Vrednost je APEX enotah."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:111 plugins/taglib/taglib-plugin.cc:71
msgid "Artist"
msgstr "Izvajalec"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:111
msgid ""
"Name of the camera owner, photographer or image creator. The detailed format is not specified, but it is "
"recommended that the information be written for ease of Interoperability. When the field is left blank, "
"it is treated as unknown."
msgstr ""
"Ime lastnika aparata, fotografa ali ustvarjalca slike. Podroben zapis ni določen, vendar je priporočeno, "
"da se podatek vpiše zaradi lažjega vzajemnega delovanja. Prazno polje določa vrednost neznanega podatka."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:112
msgid "Battery Level"
msgstr "Polnost baterije"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:112
msgid "Battery level."
msgstr "Polnost baterije."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:113
msgid "Bits per Sample"
msgstr "Bitov na vzorec"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:113
msgid ""
"The number of bits per image component. Each component of the image is 8 bits, so the value for this tag "
"is 8. In JPEG compressed data a JPEG marker is used instead of this tag."
msgstr ""
"Število bitov na enoto slike. Vsaka enota slike ima 8 bitov, zato je vrednost oznake 8. Pri stisnjenih "
"datotekah JPEG je uporabljena oznaka JPEG namesto te oznake."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:114
msgid "Brightness"
msgstr "Svetlost"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:114
msgid ""
"The value of brightness. The unit is the APEX value. Ordinarily it is given in the range of -99.99 to "
"99.99."
msgstr "Vrednosti osvetlitve so v APEX enotah. Vrednost se vrednost med -99.99 in 99.99."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:115 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:159
msgid "CFA Pattern"
msgstr "CFA Vzorec"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:115 plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:159
msgid ""
"The color filter array (CFA) geometric pattern of the image sensor when a one-chip color area sensor is "
"used. It does not apply to all sensing methods."
msgstr ""
"Geometrična vrsta vzorca barvnega filtra (CFA) barvnega tipala, kadar je uporabljen čip z enim tipalom za "
"barve in zato ni določen za vse metode zaznavanja."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:116
msgid "CFA Repeat Pattern Dim"
msgstr "CFA ponavljalni vzorec zameglitve"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:116
msgid "CFA Repeat Pattern Dim."
msgstr "CFA ponavljalni vzorec zameglitve."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:117
msgid "Components Configuration"
msgstr "Nastavitev enot"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:117
msgid ""
"Information specific to compressed data. The channels of each component are arranged in order from the "
"1st component to the 4th. For uncompressed data the data arrangement is given in the "
"<Exif.PhotometricInterpretation> tag. However, since <Exif.PhotometricInterpretation> can only express "
"the order of Y, Cb and Cr, this tag is provided for cases when compressed data uses components other than "
"Y, Cb, and Cr and to enable support of other sequences."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnosti značilne za stisnjene podatke. Vrednosti posamezne barve so urejene v vrsti od prve do "
"četrte. Nestisnjeni podatki so urejeni v oznaki <Exif.PhotometricInterpretation>, vendar pa so urejeni le "
"v vrsti Y, Cb in Cr. Zato oznaka določa le podatke stisnjenih slik, ki uporabljajo druge sheme zaporedij "
"barv."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:118
msgid "Compressed Bits per Pixel"
msgstr "Stisnjenost v bitih na točko"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:118
msgid ""
"Information specific to compressed data. The compression mode used for a compressed image is indicated in "
"unit bits per pixel."
msgstr ""
"Podrobnosti določene za stisnjene podatke. Uporabljen način stiskanja je določen kot bitne enote na točko."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:119
msgid "Compression"
msgstr "Stiskanje"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:119
msgid ""
"The compression scheme used for the image data. When a primary image is JPEG compressed, this designation "
"is not necessary and is omitted. When thumbnails use JPEG compression, this tag value is set to 6."
msgstr ""
"Shema stiskanja za slikovne podatke. Kadar je osnovna slika stisnjena v JPEG načinu, določilo ni obvezno "
"in ga lahko izpustimo. V primeru, da je JPEG stiskanje uporabljeno za sličice, je določena vrednost 6."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:120
msgid "Contrast"
msgstr "Kontrast"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:120
msgid "The direction of contrast processing applied by the camera when the image was shot."
msgstr "Smer obdelave kontrasta slike, ki ga predoči aparat ob zajemanju slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:121
msgid "Date and Time (digitized)"
msgstr "Datum in čas (digitalizirano)"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:121
msgid "The date and time when the image was stored as digital data."
msgstr "Datum in čas shranjevanja slike v digitalni obliki."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:122
msgid "Date and Time (original)"
msgstr "Datum in čas (originalno)"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:122
msgid ""
"The date and time when the original image data was generated. For a digital still camera the date and "
"time the picture was taken are recorded."
msgstr ""
"Datum in čas shranjevanja originalne slike. Pri zajemanju slike s fotoaparatom sta datum in čas določena "
"kot datum in čas zajetja slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:123
msgid "Device Setting Description"
msgstr "Opis nastavitev naprave"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:123
msgid ""
"Information on the picture-taking conditions of a particular camera model. The tag is used only to "
"indicate the picture-taking conditions in the reader."
msgstr "Podrobnosti pogojev zajemanja posameznega aparata."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:124
msgid "Digital Zoom Ratio"
msgstr "Raven digitalnega približanja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:124
msgid ""
"The digital zoom ratio when the image was shot. If the numerator of the recorded value is 0, this "
"indicates that digital zoom was not used."
msgstr ""
"Razmerje digitalnega približanja ob zajetju slike. Številčna vrednost enaka 0 določa, da digitalno "
"približanje ni bilo uporabljena. "

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:125
msgid "Exif Version"
msgstr "Exif različica"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:125
msgid ""
"The version of Exif standard supported. Nonexistence of this field is taken to mean nonconformance to the "
"standard."
msgstr "Določa podporo Exif standardu. V primeru, da polje ni določeno, standard Exif ni podprt."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:126
msgid "Exposure Index"
msgstr "Indeks osvetlitve"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:126
msgid "The exposure index selected on the camera or input device at the time the image is captured."
msgstr "Zapis indeksa osvetlitve zabeleženega ob zajetju slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:127
msgid "Exposure time, given in seconds."
msgstr "Čas osvetlitve določen v sekundah."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:128
msgid "File Source"
msgstr "Vir datoteke"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:128
msgid ""
"Indicates the image source. If a DSC recorded the image, this tag value of this tag always be set to 3, "
"indicating that the image was recorded on a DSC."
msgstr "Določa vir slike. V primeru, da je slika zajeta na sistemu DSC, je vrednost oznake 3."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:129
msgid "Fill Order"
msgstr "Vrstni red polnjenja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:129
msgid "Fill order."
msgstr "Vrstni red polnjenja."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:130
msgid "FlashPix Version"
msgstr "Različica FlashPix"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:130
msgid "The FlashPix format version supported by a FPXR file."
msgstr "Zapis FlashPix različice je podprt preko datoteke FPXR."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:131
msgid "Focal Length In 35mm Film"
msgstr "Žariščna razdalja 35 mm filma"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:131
msgid ""
"The equivalent focal length assuming a 35mm film camera, in mm. A value of 0 means the focal length is "
"unknown. Note that this tag differs from the <Exif.FocalLength> tag."
msgstr ""
"Žariščna razdalja, privzeto predvidena za 35mm filmsko kamero. Vrednost 0 mm predstavlja neznano "
"vrednost. Ta oznaka ni enaka oznaki <Exif.FocalLength>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:132
msgid "Focal Plane Resolution Unit"
msgstr "Enota ploskovne ločljivosti žarišča"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:132
msgid ""
"The unit for measuring <Exif.FocalPlaneXResolution> and <Exif.FocalPlaneYResolution>. This value is the "
"same as the <Exif.ResolutionUnit>."
msgstr ""
"Enota za merjenje <Exif.FocalPlaneXResolution> in <Exif.FocalPlaneYResolution>. Vrednost je enaka "
"vrednosti <Exif.ResolutionUnit>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:133
msgid "Focal Plane x-Resolution"
msgstr "Ploskev žariščne ločljivosti X"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:133
msgid ""
"The number of pixels in the image width (X) direction per <Exif.FocalPlaneResolutionUnit> on the camera "
"focal plane."
msgstr "Število točk širine slike (X) za <Exif.FocalPlaneResolutionUnit> na ploskovnem žarišču aparata."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:134
msgid "Focal Plane y-Resolution"
msgstr "Ploskev žariščne ločljivosti Y"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:134
msgid ""
"The number of pixels in the image height (Y) direction per <Exif.FocalPlaneResolutionUnit> on the camera "
"focal plane."
msgstr "Število točk višine slike (Y) za <Exif.FocalPlaneResolutionUnit> na ploskovnem žarišču aparata."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:135
msgid "Gain Control"
msgstr "Nadzor okrepitve"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:135
msgid "This tag indicates the degree of overall image gain adjustment."
msgstr "Oznaka določa raven splošne prilagoditve okrepitve slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:136
msgid "Gamma"
msgstr "Gama"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:136
msgid "Indicates the value of coefficient gamma."
msgstr "Določa vrednost barvnega koeficienta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:137
msgid "Altitude"
msgstr "Nadmorska višina"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:137
msgid ""
"Indicates the altitude based on the reference in <Exif.GPS.AltitudeRef>. The reference unit is meters."
msgstr "Določa nadmorsko višino glede na <Exif.GPS.AltitudeRef>. Vrednost enot je v metrih."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:138
msgid "Altitude Reference"
msgstr "Vrednost nadmorske višine"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:138
msgid ""
"Indicates the altitude used as the reference altitude. If the reference is sea level and the altitude is "
"above sea level, 0 is given. If the altitude is below sea level, a value of 1 is given and the altitude "
"is indicated as an absolute value in the <Exif.GPS.Altitude> tag. The reference unit is meters."
msgstr ""
"Določa nadmorsko višino kot referenčno vrednost. V primeru, da je referenčna vrednost nadmorska višina, "
"dejanska pa je nad to vrednostjo, se zabeleži vrednost 0. Nadmorska višina pod ravnjo gladine morja "
"določi vrednost 1, dejanska vrednost pa se zabeleži kot absolutna vrednost v oznaki <Exif.GPS.Altitude>. "
"Vrednost je v metrih."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:139
msgid "GPS Info IFDPointer"
msgstr "GPS Info IFDPointer"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:139
msgid ""
"A pointer to the GPS Info IFD. The Interoperability structure of the GPS Info IFD, like that of Exif IFD, "
"has no image data."
msgstr ""
"Kazalnik na GPS podrobnosti IFD. Vrednost vzajemnega delovanja zgradbe GPS podrobnosti IFD, kot Exif IFD, "
"ne vsebuje podatkov slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:140
msgid "Latitude"
msgstr "Zemljepisna širina"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:140
msgid ""
"Indicates the latitude. The latitude is expressed as three RATIONAL values giving the degrees, minutes, "
"and seconds, respectively. When degrees, minutes and seconds are expressed, the format is dd/1,mm/1,ss/1. "
"When degrees and minutes are used and, for example, fractions of minutes are given up to two decimal "
"places, the format is dd/1,mmmm/100,0/1."
msgstr ""
"Določa geografsko širino, ki je izražena s tremi racionalnimi vrednostmi ločeno za stopinje, minute in "
"sekunde. Zapis je poenoten na dd/1,mm/1,ss/1. Podrobneje pa je mogoče zapis oblikovati z deleži dd/1,mmmm/"
"100,0/1."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:141
msgid "North or South Latitude"
msgstr "Severna ali južna zemljepisna širina"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:141
msgid ""
"Indicates whether the latitude is north or south latitude. The ASCII value “N” indicates north latitude, "
"and “S” is south latitude."
msgstr ""
"Določa zemljepisno širino kot sever in jug. ASCII vrednost »N« določa severno zemljepisno širino in "
"vrednost »S« južno."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:142
msgid "Longitude"
msgstr "Zemljepisna dolžina"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:142
msgid ""
"Indicates the longitude. The longitude is expressed as three RATIONAL values giving the degrees, minutes, "
"and seconds, respectively. When degrees, minutes and seconds are expressed, the format is ddd/1,mm/1,ss/"
"1. When degrees and minutes are used and, for example, fractions of minutes are given up to two decimal "
"places, the format is ddd/1,mmmm/100,0/1."
msgstr ""
"Določa geografsko dolžino, ki je izražena s tremi racionalnimi vrednostmi ločeno za stopinje, minute in "
"sekunde. Zapis je poenoten na dd/1,mm/1,ss/1. Podrobneje pa je mogoče zapis oblikovati z deleži dd/1,mmmm/"
"100,0/1."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:143
msgid "East or West Longitude"
msgstr "Vzhodna ali zahodna zemljepisna dolžina"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:143
msgid ""
"Indicates whether the longitude is east or west longitude. ASCII “E” indicates east longitude, and “W” is "
"west longitude."
msgstr ""
"Določa, ali je zemljepisna dolžina vzhodno in zahodno. ASCII vrednost »E« določa vzhodno zemljepisno "
"dolžino, vrednost »W« zahodno."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:144
msgid "GPS Tag Version"
msgstr "Različica oznake GPS"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:144
msgid ""
"Indicates the version of <Exif.GPS.InfoIFD>. This tag is mandatory when <Exif.GPS.Info> tag is present."
msgstr ""
"Določa različico <Exif.GPS.InfoIFD>. Oznaka je obvezna v primeru, če je določena tudi vrednost "
"<Exif.GPS.Info>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:145
msgid "Image Description"
msgstr "Opis slike"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:145
msgid ""
"A character string giving the title of the image. Two-bytes character codes cannot be used. When a 2-"
"bytes code is necessary, the Exif Private tag <Exif.UserComment> is to be used."
msgstr ""
"Znakovni niz naslova slike v 2-bitni znakovni kodi. Pri uporabi te vrste kode je uporabljena tudi oznaka "
"<Exif.UserComment>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:146
msgid "Image Resources Block"
msgstr "Izvorni blok slike"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:146
msgid "Image Resources Block."
msgstr "Izvorni blok slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:147
msgid "Image Unique ID"
msgstr "Enovit ID slike"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:147
msgid ""
"This tag indicates an identifier assigned uniquely to each image. It is recorded as an ASCII string "
"equivalent to hexadecimal notation and 128-bit fixed length."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka določa enoznačno določilo slike. Določilo je shranjeno v obliki ASCII niza enakega šestnajstiški "
"vrednosti 128 bitne dolžine."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:148
msgid "Inter Color Profile"
msgstr "Barvni profil Inter"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:148
msgid "Inter Color Profile."
msgstr "Barvni profil Inter."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:149
msgid "Interoperability Index"
msgstr "Indeks vzajemnosti"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:149
msgid "Indicates the identification of the Interoperability rule. Use “R98” for stating ExifR98 Rules."
msgstr "Določa pravila vzajemnosti delovanja. Možnost »R98« omogoči zagon pravil ExifR98."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:150
msgid "Interoperability Version"
msgstr "Različica vzajemnosti"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:150
msgid "Interoperability version."
msgstr "Različica vzajemnosti."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:151
msgid "IPTC/NAA"
msgstr "IPTC/NAA"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:151
msgid "An IPTC/NAA record."
msgstr "Zapis IPTC/NAA."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:152
msgid "JPEG Interchange Format"
msgstr "Menjalni JPEG zapis"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:152
msgid ""
"The offset to the start byte (SOI) of JPEG compressed thumbnail data. This is not used for primary image "
"JPEG data."
msgstr ""
"Zamik do začetnega bita (SOI) pri JPEG stisnjenih podatkih sličic. Možnost ni v uporabi pri osnovnih "
"slikah."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:153
msgid "JPEG Interchange Format Length"
msgstr "Dolžina menjalnega JPEG zapisa"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:153
msgid ""
"The number of bytes of JPEG compressed thumbnail data. This is not used for primary image JPEG data. JPEG "
"thumbnails are not divided but are recorded as a continuous JPEG bitstream from SOI to EOI. Appn and COM "
"markers should not be recorded. Compressed thumbnails must be recorded in no more than 64 Kbytes, "
"including all other data to be recorded in APP1."
msgstr ""
"Število bajtov stisnjenih podatkov JPEG sličic. Možnost se ne uporablja pri osnovni velikosti JPEG slike. "
"Sličice JPEG niso razdeljene ampak so posnete kot nadaljujoči se JPEG pretok od SOI do EOI. Appn in COM "
"markerji niso posneti. Stisnjene sličice ne smejo biti večje od 64 kilobajtov, vključno z ostalimi "
"podatki, ki so posneti v APP1."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:154
msgid "JPEG Procedure"
msgstr "JPEG Procedura"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:154
msgid "JPEG procedure."
msgstr "Postopek JPEG."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:155
msgid "Light Source"
msgstr "Vir svetlobe"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:155
msgid "The kind of light source."
msgstr "Vrsta vira svetlobe."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:156
msgid "Manufacturer"
msgstr "Proizvajalec"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:156
msgid ""
"The manufacturer of the recording equipment. This is the manufacturer of the DSC, scanner, video "
"digitizer or other equipment that generated the image. When the field is left blank, it is treated as "
"unknown."
msgstr ""
"Proizvajalec naprave za snemanje, podrobneje DSC, optičnega bralnika, video digitalnika in drugih naprav, "
"ki so ustvarile sliko. Prazno polje določa neznano vrednost."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:157
msgid "Maker Note"
msgstr "Beležnica"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:157
msgid ""
"A tag for manufacturers of Exif writers to record any desired information. The contents are up to the "
"manufacturer."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka za proizvajalce Exif zapisovalcev za shranjevanje želenih podrobnosti o sliki. Vsebino določajo "
"proizvajalci."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:158
msgid ""
"The model name or model number of the equipment. This is the model name or number of the DSC, scanner, "
"video digitizer or other equipment that generated the image. When the field is left blank, it is treated "
"as unknown."
msgstr ""
"Ime ali številka modela naprave. Sem sodijo oznake DSC, optičnih bralnikov, video digitalnika in drugih "
"naprav, ki so ustvarile sliko. Prazno polje se obravnava kot neznana vrednost."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:160
msgid "New Subfile Type"
msgstr "Nova vrsta prikazne datoteke"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:160
msgid "A general indication of the kind of data contained in this subfile."
msgstr "Splošna navedba vrste podatkov zapisanih v prikazni datoteki"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:161
msgid "OECF"
msgstr "OECF"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:161
msgid ""
"The Opto-Electronic Conversion Function (OECF) specified in ISO 14524. <Exif.OECF> is the relationship "
"between the camera optical input and the image values."
msgstr ""
"Opto-Elektronska funkcija pretvorbe (OECF) določena z ISO 14524. <Exif.OECF> predstavlja povezavo med "
"optičnim zajemanjem aparata in vrednostim slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:162
msgid "The image orientation viewed in terms of rows and columns."
msgstr "Usmerjenost slike določeno z vrsticami n stolpci."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:163
msgid "Photometric Interpretation"
msgstr "Fotometrično tolmačenje"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:163
msgid "The pixel composition. In JPEG compressed data a JPEG marker is used instead of this tag."
msgstr "Zgradba točke slike. Pri JPEG stiskanju je uporabljen poseben marker namesto te oznake."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:164
msgid "Planar Configuration"
msgstr "Nastavitev ravnine"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:164
msgid ""
"Indicates whether pixel components are recorded in a chunky or planar format. In JPEG compressed files a "
"JPEG marker is used instead of this tag. If this field does not exist, the TIFF default of 1 (chunky) is "
"assumed."
msgstr ""
"Določa kako so točke v sliki shranjene. Pri stisnjenih JPEG zapisih slik je namesto te oznake uporabljen "
"marker. V primeru, da to polje ne obstaja, je določena privzeta TIFF vrednost 1."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:165
msgid "Primary Chromaticities"
msgstr "Osnovna barvitost"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:165
msgid ""
"The chromaticity of the three primary colors of the image. Normally this tag is not necessary, since "
"colorspace is specified in <Exif.ColorSpace> tag."
msgstr ""
"Barvitost osnovnih treh barv slike. Običajno je oznaka izpuščena, saj je barvni prostor določen v oznaki "
"<Exif.ColorSpace>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:166
msgid "Reference Black/White"
msgstr "Sklicna črnina/belina"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:166
msgid ""
"The reference black point value and reference white point value. No defaults are given in TIFF, but the "
"values below are given as defaults here. The color space is declared in a color space information tag, "
"with the default being the value that gives the optimal image characteristics under these conditions."
msgstr ""
"Referenčni vrednosti črne in bele točke. Privzetih vrednosti za TIFF ni, so pa te določene spodaj. Barvno "
"polje določa vrednost, ki najbolj ustreza pogojem prikazovanja."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:167
msgid "Related Image File Format"
msgstr "Skladna oblika zapisa slikovne datoteke"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:167
msgid "Related image file format."
msgstr "Privzeti slikovni zapis datoteke."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:168
msgid "Related Image Length"
msgstr "Skladna dolžina slike"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:168
msgid "Related image length."
msgstr "Po razmerju določena dolžina slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:169
msgid "Related Image Width"
msgstr "Skladna širina slike"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:169
msgid "Related image width."
msgstr "Po razmerju določena širina slike."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:170
msgid "Related Sound File"
msgstr "Sorodna zvočna datoteka"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:170
msgid ""
"This tag is used to record the name of an audio file related to the image data. The only relational "
"information recorded here is the Exif audio file name and extension (an ASCII string consisting of 8 "
"characters + “.” + 3 characters). The path is not recorded. When using this tag, audio files must be "
"recorded in conformance to the Exif audio format. Writers are also allowed to store the data such as "
"Audio within APP2 as FlashPix extension stream data. Audio files must be recorded in conformance to the "
"Exif audio format. If multiple files are mapped to one file, the above format is used to record just one "
"audio file name. If there are multiple audio files, the first recorded file is given. When there are "
"three Exif audio files “SND00001.WAV”, “SND00002.WAV” and “SND00003.WAV”, the Exif image file name for "
"each of them, “DSC00001.JPG”, is indicated. By combining multiple relational information, a variety of "
"playback possibilities can be supported. The method of using relational information is left to the "
"implementation on the playback side. Since this information is an ASCII character string, it is "
"terminated by NULL. When this tag is used to map audio files, the relation of the audio file to image "
"data must also be indicated on the audio file end."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka se uporablja za zapis imena zvočne datoteke, povezane s slikovnimi podatki. Edina relacijska "
"informacija, ki se zapiše na tem mestu, je ime zvočne datoteke Exif in razširitev (niz ASCII, sestavljen "
"iz 8 znakov + \".\" + 3 znaki). Pot se ne vpiše. Pri uporabi te oznake morajo biti zvočne datoteke "
"zapisane v skladu z zvočnim formatom Exif. Zapisovalci lahko podatke, kot je Audio, shranijo tudi v APP2 "
"kot podatke toka z razširitvijo FlashPix. Zvočne datoteke morajo biti zapisane v skladu z zvočnim "
"formatom Exif. Če je več datotek preslikanih v eno datoteko, se zgornji format uporabi za zapis samo "
"enega imena zvočne datoteke. Če je zvočnih datotek več, se navede prva zapisana datoteka. Če obstajajo "
"tri zvočne datoteke Exif \"SND00001.WAV\", \"SND00002.WAV\" in \"SND00003.WAV\", je navedeno ime slikovne "
"datoteke Exif za vsako od njih, \"DSC00001.JPG\". Z združevanjem več relacijskih informacij je mogoče "
"podpirati različne možnosti predvajanja. Način uporabe relacijskih informacij je prepuščen izvedbi na "
"strani predvajanja. Ker so te informacije niz znakov ASCII, se končajo z NULL. Kadar se ta oznaka "
"uporablja za preslikavo zvočnih datotek, je treba na koncu zvočne datoteke navesti tudi razmerje med "
"zvočno datoteko in slikovnimi podatki."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:171
msgid "Resolution Unit"
msgstr "Enota ločljivosti"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:171
msgid ""
"The unit for measuring <Exif.XResolution> and <Exif.YResolution>. The same unit is used for both "
"<Exif.XResolution> and <Exif.YResolution>. If the image resolution is unknown, 2 (inches) is designated."
msgstr ""
"Enota za merjenje <Exif.XResolution> in <Exif.YResolution>. Enaka enota je določena za obe vrednosti. V "
"primeru, da ločljivost slike ni znana, je določena vrednost 5.1 centimetra."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:172
msgid "Rows per Strip"
msgstr "Vrstice na trak slike"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:172
msgid ""
"The number of rows per strip. This is the number of rows in the image of one strip when an image is "
"divided into strips. With JPEG compressed data this designation is not needed and is omitted."
msgstr ""
"Število vrstic na trak slike določa število vrstic slike, ki določajo en trak, v primeru, da je slika na "
"trakove razdeljena. Pri JPEG stiskanju ta vrednost ni zahtevana in se ne beleži."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:173
msgid "Samples per Pixel"
msgstr "Vzorci na točko"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:173
msgid ""
"The number of components per pixel. Since this standard applies to RGB and YCbCr images, the value set "
"for this tag is 3. In JPEG compressed data a JPEG marker is used instead of this tag."
msgstr ""
"Število enot na točko slike. Ker standard določa RGB in YCbCr barvne sheme slik, je vrednost oznake "
"določena s 3. Pri JPEG stiskanju podatkov se namesto te oznake uporablja JPEG marker."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:174
msgid "Saturation"
msgstr "Nasičenost"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:174
msgid "The direction of saturation processing applied by the camera when the image was shot."
msgstr "Smer zasičenosti slike med zajemanjem."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:175
msgid "Scene Capture Type"
msgstr "Vrsta zajema scene"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:175
msgid ""
"The type of scene that was shot. It can also be used to record the mode in which the image was shot. Note "
"that this differs from <Exif.SceneType> tag."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta slikane scene. Lahko se uporablja kot oznaka načina zajemanja slike. Oznaka ni enaka oznaki "
"<Exif.SceneType>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:176
msgid "Scene Type"
msgstr "Vrsta scene"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:176
msgid ""
"The type of scene. If a DSC recorded the image, this tag value must always be set to 1, indicating that "
"the image was directly photographed."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta slikane scene. V primeru, da je slika zajeta z DSC, mora biti vrednost določena kot 1, kar določa, "
"da je bila slika neposredno zajeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:177
msgid "Sensing Method"
msgstr "Metoda zaznavanja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:177
msgid "The image sensor type on the camera or input device."
msgstr "Vrsta tipala na aparatu."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:178
msgid "Sharpness"
msgstr "Ostrina"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:178
msgid "The direction of sharpness processing applied by the camera when the image was shot."
msgstr "Smer ostritve, ki jo je zabeležil aparat med zajemanjem slike.."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:179
msgid ""
"This tag records the name and version of the software or firmware of the camera or image input device "
"used to generate the image. When the field is left blank, it is treated as unknown."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka vsebuje podatke o imenu in različici programske opreme aparata ali druge naprave s katero je bila "
"ustvarjena slika. Prazno polje določa neznano vrednost."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:180
msgid "Spatial Frequency Response"
msgstr "Odziv prostorske frekvence"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:180
msgid ""
"This tag records the camera or input device spatial frequency table and SFR values in the direction of "
"image width, image height, and diagonal direction, as specified in ISO 12233."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka vsebuje podatke aparata o prostorski frekvenci in SFR vrednostih v smeri širine, višine in "
"diagonale slike, kot je določeno v ISO 12233."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:181
msgid "Spectral Sensitivity"
msgstr "Spektralna občutljivost"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:181
msgid "The spectral sensitivity of each channel of the camera used."
msgstr "Spektralna občutljivost posameznega kanala aparata."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:182
msgid "Strip Byte Count"
msgstr "Števec bajtov trakov"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:182
msgid ""
"The total number of bytes in each strip. With JPEG compressed data this designation is not needed and is "
"omitted."
msgstr "Skupno število bajtov v vsakem traku. Pri JPEG stiskanju ta oznaka ni zahtevana in se ne beleži."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:183
msgid "Strip Offsets"
msgstr "Zamik trakov"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:183
msgid ""
"For each strip, the byte offset of that strip. It is recommended that this be selected so the number of "
"strip bytes does not exceed 64 Kbytes. With JPEG compressed data this designation is not needed and is "
"omitted."
msgstr ""
"Za vsak trak določen zamik začetka traku. Priporočljivo je, da je vrednost bajtov traku ne presega 64 "
"kilobajtov podatkov. Pri JPEG stiskanju podatkov vrednost ni zahtevana in se ne beleži."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:184
msgid "Sub IFD Offsets"
msgstr "SubIFD zamik"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:184
msgid "Defined by Adobe Corporation to enable TIFF Trees within a TIFF file."
msgstr "Določen preko Adobe standarda, da omogoči TIFF zgradbo znotraj TIFF datoteke."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:185
msgid "Subject Area"
msgstr "Območje predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:185
msgid "The location and area of the main subject in the overall scene."
msgstr "Lega in območje glavnega predmeta na skupni sceni."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:186
msgid "Subject Distance"
msgstr "Oddaljenost predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:186
msgid "The distance to the subject, given in meters."
msgstr "Razdalja do predmeta določena v metrih."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:187
msgid "Subject Distance Range"
msgstr "Oddaljenost območja predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:187
msgid "The distance to the subject."
msgstr "Razdalja do predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:188
msgid "Subject Location"
msgstr "Mesto predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:188
msgid ""
"The location of the main subject in the scene. The value of this tag represents the pixel at the center "
"of the main subject relative to the left edge, prior to rotation processing as per the <Exif.Rotation> "
"tag. The first value indicates the X column number and second indicates the Y row number."
msgstr ""
"Lega glavnega predmeta na skupni sceni. Vrednost oznake predstavlja točko v središču glavnega predmeta "
"glede na levi rob, pred obračanjem slike določenim v oznaki <Exif.Rotation>. Prva vrednost določa stolpec "
"X, druga pa vrstico Y."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:189
msgid "Subsec Time"
msgstr "Delež časa"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:189
msgid "Fractions of seconds for the <Exif.DateTime> tag."
msgstr "Del sekunde za oznako <Exif.DateTime>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:190
msgid "Subsec Time Digitized"
msgstr "Delež časa digitaliziranja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:190
msgid "Fractions of seconds for the <Exif.DateTimeDigitized> tag."
msgstr "Del sekunde za oznako <Exif.DateTimeDigitized>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:191
msgid "Subsec Time Original"
msgstr "Delež časa osnove"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:191
msgid "Fractions of seconds for the <Exif.DateTimeOriginal> tag."
msgstr "Del sekunde za oznako <Exif.DateTimeOriginal>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:192
msgid "TIFF/EP Standard ID"
msgstr "TIFF/EP Standard ID"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:192
msgid "TIFF/EP Standard ID."
msgstr "TIFF/EP Standard ID."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:193
msgid "Transfer Function"
msgstr "Funkcija prenosa"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:193
msgid ""
"A transfer function for the image, described in tabular style. Normally this tag is not necessary, since "
"color space is specified in <Exif.ColorSpace> tag."
msgstr ""
"Funkcija prenosa slike, opisana v razpredelnici. Običajno oznaka ni zahtevana, saj je barvni prostor "
"določen v oznaki <Exif.ColorSpace>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:194
msgid "Transfer Range"
msgstr "Območje prenosa"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:194
msgid "Transfer range."
msgstr "Območje prenosa."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:195
msgid "White Point"
msgstr "Bela točka"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:195
msgid ""
"The chromaticity of the white point of the image. Normally this tag is not necessary, since color space "
"is specified in <Exif.ColorSpace> tag."
msgstr ""
"Barvitost belih točk na sliki. Običajno oznaka ni zahtevana, saj je barvni prostor določen v oznaki "
"<Exif.ColorSpace>."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:196
msgid "XML Packet"
msgstr "Paket XML"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:196
msgid "XMP metadata."
msgstr "Metapodatki XMP."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:197
msgid "YCbCr Coefficients"
msgstr "Koeficient YCbCr"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:197
msgid ""
"The matrix coefficients for transformation from RGB to YCbCr image data. No default is given in TIFF; but "
"here “Color Space Guidelines” is used as the default. The color space is declared in a color space "
"information tag, with the default being the value that gives the optimal image characteristics under this "
"condition."
msgstr ""
"Matrični koeficienti pretvarjanja RGB v YCbCr barvni sistem slike. Privzeta vrednost v TIFF ni določena; "
"je pa privzeta vrednost določena v polju \"Vodila barvnega prostora\". Barvni prostor je določan v ločeni "
"oznaki, privzeta vrednost pa je tista, ki najbolje podpira pogoje vzajemnega delovanja."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:198
msgid "YCbCr Positioning"
msgstr "YCbCr prilagajanje"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:198
msgid ""
"The position of chrominance components in relation to the luminance component. This field is designated "
"only for JPEG compressed data or uncompressed YCbCr data. The TIFF default is 1 (centered); but when "
"Y:Cb:Cr = 4:2:2 it is recommended that 2 (co-sited) be used to record data, in order to improve the image "
"quality when viewed on TV systems. When this field does not exist, the reader shall assume the TIFF "
"default. In the case of Y:Cb:Cr = 4:2:0, the TIFF default (centered) is recommended. If the reader does "
"not have the capability of supporting both kinds of <Exif.YCbCrPositioning>, it shall follow the TIFF "
"default regardless of the value in this field. It is preferable that readers be able to support both "
"centered and co-sited positioning."
msgstr ""
"Lega barvitosti v povezavi z osvetljenostjo slike. Polje določa vrednost le za stisnjene JPEG podatke ali "
"nestisnjene podatke YCbCr. Privzeta TIFF vrednosti je 1 (sredinjeno); vendar je priporočena za razmerje "
"Y:Cb:Cr = 4:2:2 vrednost 2 za shranjevanje podatkov, z namenom izboljšanja kakovosti slike pri "
"pregledovanju preko TV zaslonov. V primeru, da polje ne obstaja, bralnik slik privzame vrednost 1. V "
"primeru razmerja Y:Cb:Cr = 4:2:0, je prav tako priporočena vrednost 1. V primeru, da bralnik slik ne "
"podpira obeh vrst podatkov <Exif.YCbCrPositioning>, sledi privzeti TIFF vrednosti neodvisno od vrednosti "
"polja."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:199
msgid "YCbCr Sub-Sampling"
msgstr "YCbCr vzorčenje"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:199
msgid ""
"The sampling ratio of chrominance components in relation to the luminance component. In JPEG compressed "
"data a JPEG marker is used instead of this tag."
msgstr ""
"Razmerje vzorčenja barvitosti barvnih delov v razmerju z osvetljenostjo. Pri stisnjenih JPEG podatkih se "
"namesto te vrednosti uporablja JPEG marker."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:201
msgid "By-line"
msgstr "Vrstično"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:201
msgid ""
"Name of the creator of the object, e.g. writer, photographer or graphic artist (multiple values allowed)."
msgstr "Ime ustvarjalca predmeta, primer: pisatelj, fotograf, umetnik (dovoljenih več vnosov)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:202
msgid "By-line Title"
msgstr "Vrstična oznaka"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:202
msgid "Title of the creator or creators of the object."
msgstr "Naslov ustvarjalca ali ustvarjalcev predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:203
msgid "Caption, Abstract"
msgstr "Naslov, povzetek"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:203 plugins/taglib/taglib-plugin.cc:337
msgid "A textual description of the data."
msgstr "Besedilni opis podatkov."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:204
msgid "Headline"
msgstr "Naslovna vrstica"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:204
msgid "A publishable entry providing a synopsis of the contents of the object."
msgstr "Objavljen vnos, ki ponuja strnjen povzetek vsebine predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:205
msgid "Sub-location"
msgstr "Podrejeno mesto"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:205
msgid "The location within a city from which the object originates."
msgstr "Podrobni podatki o mestu, kjer je bil predmet ustvarjen."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:206
msgid "City"
msgstr "Mesto"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:206
msgid "City of object origin."
msgstr "Mesto izvora predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:207
msgid "Province, State"
msgstr "Provinca, Država"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:207
msgid "The Province/State where the object originates."
msgstr "Okraj ali območje od koder predmet izvira."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:208
msgid "Country Code"
msgstr "Koda države"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:208
msgid "The code of the country/primary location where the object was created."
msgstr "Koda države ali kraja, kjer je bil predmet ustvarjen."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:209
msgid "Country Name"
msgstr "Ime države"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:209
msgid "The name of the country/primary location where the object was created."
msgstr "Ime države ali kraja, kjer je bil predmet ustvarjen."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:210 plugins/taglib/taglib-plugin.cc:336
msgid "Contact"
msgstr "Stik"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:210
msgid ""
"The person or organization which can provide further background information on the object (multiple "
"values allowed)."
msgstr "Oseba ali organizacija, ki lahko ponudi več podrobnosti o predmetu (dovoljenih več vnosov)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:211
msgid "Copyright Notice"
msgstr "Sporočilo avtorskih pravic"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:211
msgid "Any necessary copyright notice."
msgstr "Vsako obvezno opozorilo avtorskih pravic."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:212
msgid "Credit"
msgstr "Zasluge"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:212
msgid "Identifies the provider of the object, not necessarily the owner/creator."
msgstr "Določa ponudnika predmeta in ne nujno lastnika ali ustvarjalca."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:213
msgid "Used to indicate specific information retrieval words (multiple values allowed)."
msgstr "Uporabljen za določitev posebnih podrobnosti pridobivanja besed (dovoljenih več vnosov)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:214
msgid "Digital Creation Date"
msgstr "Datum digitaliziranja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:214
msgid "The date the digital representation of the object was created."
msgstr "Datum, ko je bila digitalna predstavitev ustvarjena."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:215
msgid "Digital Creation Time"
msgstr "Čas digitaliziranja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:215
msgid "The time the digital representation of the object was created."
msgstr "Čas, ko je bila digitalna predstavitev ustvarjena."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:216
msgid "Image Orientation"
msgstr "Usmerjenost slike"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:216
msgid "The layout of the image area: “P” for portrait, “L” for landscape, and “S” for square."
msgstr "Razpored območja slike: »P« portret, »L« za ležeče in »S« za kvadratno območje."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:217
msgid "Special Instructions"
msgstr "Posebna navodila"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:217
msgid "Other editorial instructions concerning the use of the object."
msgstr "Druga navodila urejevanja, ki so povezana z uporabo predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:218
msgid "Urgency"
msgstr "Nujnost"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:218
msgid ""
"Specifies the editorial urgency of content and not necessarily the envelope handling priority. “1” is "
"most urgent, “5” normal, and “8” least urgent."
msgstr ""
"Določa prednost urejanja in ne nujno upravljanja z ovojnico. Vrednost »1« pomeni nujno, »5« običajno in "
"»8« odložljivo."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:219
msgid "Action Advised"
msgstr "Priporočeno dejanje"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:219
msgid ""
"The type of action that this object provides to a previous object. “01” Object Kill, “02” Object Replace, "
"“03” Object Append, “04” Object Reference."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta dejanja, ki ga predmet ponuja glede na predhodni predmet. »01« predmet uniči, »02« predmet "
"zamenjaj, »03« predmet pripni, »04« predmet naveži."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:220
msgid "ARM Identifier"
msgstr "Določilo ARM"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:220
msgid "Identifies the Abstract Relationship Method (ARM)."
msgstr "Določa abstraktni način povezovanja (Abstract relationship method)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:221
msgid "ARM Version"
msgstr "Različica ARM"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:221
msgid "Identifies the version of the Abstract Relationship Method (ARM)."
msgstr "Določa različico abstraktnega načina povezovanja (Abstract relationship method version)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:222
msgid "Audio Duration"
msgstr "Trajanje posnetka"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:222
msgid "The running time of the audio data in the form HHMMSS."
msgstr "Trajanje predvajanja zvoka v obliki HHMMSS."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:223
msgid "Audio Outcue"
msgstr "Zvočno oddajanje"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:223
msgid "The content at the end of the audio data."
msgstr "Vsebina na koncu podatkov zvočnega posnetka."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:224
msgid "Audio Sampling Rate"
msgstr "Raven vzorčenja zvoka"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:224
msgid "The sampling rate in Hz of the audio data."
msgstr "Raven vzorčenja zvočnih podatkov v Hz."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:225
msgid "Audio Sampling Resolution"
msgstr "Ločljivost zvočnega vzorčenja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:225
msgid "The number of bits in each audio sample."
msgstr "Število bitov vsakega zvočnega vzorca."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:226
msgid "Audio Type"
msgstr "Zvočna vrsta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:226
msgid "The number of channels and type of audio (music, text, etc.) in the object."
msgstr "Število kanalov in vrsta zvočne datoteke (glasba, besedilo, ...) v predmetu."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:227 plugins/gsf/gsf-plugin.cc:69
msgid "Category"
msgstr "Kategorija"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:227
msgid "Identifies the subject of the object in the opinion of the provider (Deprecated)."
msgstr "Določa zadevo predmeta med možnostmi ponudnika (opuščeno)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:228
msgid "Coded Character Set"
msgstr "kodirani znakovni nabor"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:228
msgid "Control functions used for the announcement, invocation or designation of coded character sets."
msgstr "Nadzorne funkcije uporabljane za objavljanje, pozivanje ali označbo nabora znakov kodiranja."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:229
msgid "Confirmed Data Size"
msgstr "Potrjena velikost podatkov"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:229
msgid "Total size of the object data."
msgstr "Skupna velikost podatkov predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:230
msgid "Content Location Code"
msgstr "Koda mesta vsebine"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:230
msgid ""
"The code of a country/geographical location referenced by the content of the object (multiple values "
"allowed)."
msgstr "Koda države ali geografska lega določena v vsebini predmeta (dovoljenih več vnosov)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:231
msgid "Content Location Name"
msgstr "Ime mesta vsebine"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:231
msgid ""
"A full, publishable name of a country/geographical location referenced by the content of the object "
"(multiple values allowed)."
msgstr ""
"Polno, objavljeno ime države ali geografskega kraja, ki je določen v vsebini predmeta (dovoljenih več "
"vnosov)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:232 plugins/gsf/gsf-plugin.cc:82 plugins/poppler/poppler-plugin.cc:62
msgid "Date Created"
msgstr "Datum stvaritve"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:232
msgid ""
"The date the intellectual content of the object was created rather than the date of the creation of the "
"physical representation."
msgstr "Datum, ko je bila avtorska vsebina ustvarjena, namesto datuma dejanskega izdelka."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:233
msgid "Date Sent"
msgstr "Datum pošiljanja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:233
msgid "The day the service sent the material."
msgstr "Dan pošiljanja storitev materiala."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:234
msgid "Destination"
msgstr "Cilj"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:234
msgid "Routing information."
msgstr "Podrobnosti usmerjevalne razpredelnice."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:235
msgid "Editorial Update"
msgstr "Uredniška posodobitev"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:235
msgid ""
"The type of update this object provides to a previous object. The link to the previous object is made "
"using the ARM. “01” indicates an additional language."
msgstr ""
"Vrsta posodobitve predmeta glede na predhodni predmet. Povezava s predhodnim predmetom je ustvarjena z "
"ARM. »01» določa dodatni jezik."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:236
msgid "Edit Status"
msgstr "Stanje urejanja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:236
msgid "Status of the object, according to the practice of the provider."
msgstr "Stanje urejanja predmeta, kot ga določa ponudnik."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:237
msgid "Envelope Number"
msgstr "Številka ovojnice"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:237
msgid "A number unique for the date and the service ID."
msgstr "Enoznačna številka datuma in ID storitve."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:238
msgid "Envelope Priority"
msgstr "Prednost ovojnice"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:238
msgid ""
"Specifies the envelope handling priority and not the editorial urgency. “1” for most urgent, “5” for "
"normal, and “8” for least urgent. “9” is user-defined."
msgstr ""
"Določa prednost upravljanja z ovojnico in ne nujnost urejanja. Vrednost »1« določa nujno, »5« običajno in "
"»8« odložljivo. Vrednost »9« določa prednost po meri."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:239
msgid "Expiration Date"
msgstr "Datum preteka"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:239
msgid "Designates the latest date the provider intends the object to be used."
msgstr "Določa najpoznejši datum, do katerega je predvidena uporaba predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:240
msgid "Expiration Time"
msgstr "Čas preteka"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:240
msgid "Designates the latest time the provider intends the object to be used."
msgstr "Določa najpoznejši čas do katerega je predvidena uporaba predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:241
msgid "File Format"
msgstr "Zapis datoteke"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:241
msgid "File format of the data described by this metadata."
msgstr "Zapis datoteke in podatki opisani v metapodatkih."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:242
msgid "File Version"
msgstr "Različica datoteke"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:242
msgid "Version of the file format."
msgstr "Različica oblike datoteke."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:243
msgid "Fixture Identifier"
msgstr "Določilo osvetljevala"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:243
msgid ""
"Identifies objects that recur often and predictably, enabling users to immediately find or recall such an "
"object."
msgstr ""
"Določa predmete, ki se pojavljajo pogosto in so predvidljivi, s čimer omogoči uporabniku hitro iskanje "
"med takimi predmeti."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:244
msgid "Image Type"
msgstr "Vrsta slike"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:244
msgid "The data format of the image object."
msgstr "Podatkovni zapis slikovnega predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:245
msgid "Language Identifier"
msgstr "Določilo jezika"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:245
msgid "The major national language of the object, according to the 2-letter codes of ISO 639:1988."
msgstr "Določilo jezika predmeta v obliki dvo-črkovne kode ISO 639 standarda: 1988."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:246
msgid "Maximum Object Size"
msgstr "Največja velikost predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:246
msgid "The largest possible size of the object if the size is not known."
msgstr "Največja možna velikost predmeta v primeru, da ta ni znana."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:247
msgid "Max Subfile Size"
msgstr "Največja velikost prikazne datoteke"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:247
msgid "The maximum size for a subfile dataset containing a portion of the object data."
msgstr ""
"Največja dovoljena velikost podatkov posamezne prikazne datoteke, ki vsebujejo del podatkov predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:248
msgid "Model Version"
msgstr "Različica modela"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:248
msgid "Version of IIM part 1."
msgstr "Različica IIM del 1."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:249
msgid "Object Attribute Reference"
msgstr "Sklic atributov predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:249
msgid "Defines the nature of the object independent of the subject (multiple values allowed)."
msgstr "Določa naravo predmeta neodvisno od predmeta samega (dovoljenih več vnosov)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:250
msgid "Object Cycle"
msgstr "Kroženje predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:250
msgid "Where “a” is morning, “p” is evening, “b” is both."
msgstr "Vrednost » a « določa dopoldanski čas, » p « popoldanski, » b « obe vrednosti."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:251
msgid "Object Name"
msgstr "Ime predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:251
msgid "A shorthand reference for the object."
msgstr "Kratek sklic predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:252
msgid "Object Size Announced"
msgstr "Objavljena velikost predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:252
msgid "The total size of the object data if it is known."
msgstr "Skupna znana velikost podatkov predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:253
msgid "Object Type Reference"
msgstr "Sklic vrste predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:253
msgid "Distinguishes between different types of objects within the IIM."
msgstr "Loči med različnimi vrstami predmetov znotraj IIM."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:254
msgid "Originating Program"
msgstr "Izvorni program"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:254
msgid "The type of program used to originate the object."
msgstr "Vrsta programa s katerim je bil predmet ustvarjen."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:255
msgid "Original Transmission Reference"
msgstr "Običajni sklic prenosa"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:255
msgid "A code representing the location of original transmission."
msgstr "Koda, ki določa kraj prvotnega prenosa."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:256
msgid "Preview Data"
msgstr "Podatki predogleda"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:256
msgid "The object preview data."
msgstr "Podatki predogleda predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:257
msgid "Preview File Format"
msgstr "Oblika predogleda datoteke"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:257
msgid "Binary value indicating the file format of the object preview data."
msgstr "Dvojiška vrednost, ki določa zapis datoteke predogleda podatkov predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:258
msgid "Preview File Format Version"
msgstr "Predogled različice zapisa datoteke"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:258
msgid "The version of the preview file format."
msgstr "Različica zapisa predogleda datoteke."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:259
msgid "Product ID"
msgstr "ID izdelka"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:259
msgid "Allows a provider to identify subsets of its overall service."
msgstr "Omogoča ponudniku določiti podrejene enote skupne storitve."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:260
msgid "Program Version"
msgstr "Različica programa"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:260
msgid "The version of the originating program."
msgstr "Različica osnovnega izvornega programa."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:261
msgid "Rasterized Caption"
msgstr "Rastrska oznaka"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:261
msgid ""
"Contains rasterized object description and is used where characters that have not been coded are required "
"for the caption."
msgstr ""
"Vsebuje opis rastrskega predmeta in je uporabljen tam, kjer so znaki, ki niso kodirani, zahtevani v "
"naslovu."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:262
msgid "Record Version"
msgstr "Različica zapisa"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:262
msgid "Identifies the version of the IIM, Part 2."
msgstr "Določa različico IIM, del 2."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:263
msgid "Reference Date"
msgstr "Sklicni datum"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:263
msgid "The date of a prior envelope to which the current object refers."
msgstr "Datum predhodne ovojnice, ki ji trenutni predmet pripada."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:264
msgid "Reference Number"
msgstr "Sklicno število"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:264
msgid "The Envelope Number of a prior envelope to which the current object refers."
msgstr "Številka predhodne ovojnice, ki ji trenutni predmet pripada."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:265
msgid "Reference Service"
msgstr "Sklicna storitev"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:265
msgid "The Service Identifier of a prior envelope to which the current object refers."
msgstr "Določilo storitve predhodne ovojnice, ki ji trenutni predmet pripada."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:266 plugins/taglib/taglib-plugin.cc:94
msgid "Release Date"
msgstr "Datum objave"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:266
msgid "Designates the earliest date the provider intends the object to be used."
msgstr "Določa najpoznejši datum, do katerega je predvidena uporaba predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:267 plugins/taglib/taglib-plugin.cc:216
msgid "Release Time"
msgstr "Čas objave"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:267
msgid "Designates the earliest time the provider intends the object to be used."
msgstr "Določa najpoznejši čas, do katerega je predvidena uporaba predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:268
msgid "Service Identifier"
msgstr "Določilo storitve"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:268
msgid "Identifies the provider and product."
msgstr "Določa ponudnika in izdelek."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:269
msgid "Size Mode"
msgstr "Način velikosti"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:269
msgid "Set to 0 if the size of the object is known and 1 if not known."
msgstr "Vrednost 0 predstavlja znano velikost, vrednost 1 pa neznano."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:270
msgid "Source"
msgstr "Izvor"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:270
msgid "The original owner of the intellectual content of the object."
msgstr "Prvi lastnik avtorstva vsebine predmeta."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:271
msgid "Subfile"
msgstr "Prikazna datoteka"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:271
msgid "The object data itself. Subfiles must be sequential so that the subfiles may be reassembled."
msgstr ""
"Lastni podatki predmeta. Prikazne datoteke si morajo slediti v zaporedju, da jih je mogoče ponovno "
"sestaviti."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:272
msgid "Subject Reference"
msgstr "Sklic predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:272
msgid ""
"A structured definition of the subject matter. It must contain an IPR, an 8 digit Subject Reference "
"Number and an optional Subject Name, Subject Matter Name, and Subject Detail Name each separated by a "
"colon (:)."
msgstr ""
"Oblikovana definicija predmeta. Vsebovati mora IPR, 8 mestno referenčno število predmeta in poljubno ime "
"predmeta, enota in podrobnosti, ločene s podpičjem (:)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:273
msgid "Supplemental Category"
msgstr "Dopolnilna kategorija"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:273
msgid "Further refines the subject of the object (Deprecated)."
msgstr "Podrobneje določa naslov predmeta (opuščeno)"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:274
msgid "Time Created"
msgstr "Čas stvaritve"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:274
msgid ""
"The time the intellectual content of the object was created rather than the date of the creation of the "
"physical representation (multiple values allowed)."
msgstr ""
"Obdobje v katerem je bila ustvarjena avtorska vsebina predmeta, namesto datuma dejanskega posnetka "
"vsebine (dovoljenih več vnosov)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:275
msgid "Time Sent"
msgstr "Čas pošiljanja"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:275
msgid "The time the service sent the material."
msgstr "Čas pošiljanja materiala."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:276
msgid "Unique Name of Object"
msgstr "Enoznačno ime predmeta"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:276
msgid ""
"An eternal, globally unique identification for the object, independent of provider and for any media form."
msgstr ""
"Notranji, splošno enoznačno določilo predmeta, neodvisno od ponudnika in določeno za vsako obliko "
"predstavne vsebine."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:277
msgid "Writer/Editor"
msgstr "Pisec/Urednik"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:277
msgid ""
"The name of the person involved in the writing, editing or correcting the object or caption/abstract "
"(multiple values allowed)."
msgstr ""
"Ime osebe, ki je odgovorna za pisanje, urejanje ali popravljanje predmeta ali naslova (dovoljenih več "
"vnosov)."

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:408 src/tags/image.rs:80
msgid "Image"
msgstr "Slika"

#: plugins/exiv2/exiv2-plugin.cc:771
msgid "A plugin for extracting metadata from images using libexiv2 library."
msgstr "Vstavek za pridobivanje metapodatkov iz slik z uporabo knjižnice libexiv2."

